{"id":27987,"global_id":"Z2lkOi8vaGFja2Vyb25lL1JlcG9ydC8yNzk4Nw==","url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/27987","title":"Window Opener Property Bug","state":"Closed","substate":"resolved","readable_substate":"Resolved","created_at":"2014-09-13T17:14:26.342Z","submitted_at":"2014-09-13T17:14:26.342Z","is_member_of_team?":false,"reporter":{"disabled":false,"username":"prakharprasad","url":"/prakharprasad","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/4Qcsaci6HdNLQCPM7oBdhJYY/43e4513b9104ea0d68c9c096cea374ba8440dde3e027af5465c8771e8839a67c"},"is_me?":false,"cleared":true,"hackerone_triager":false,"hacker_mediation":false},"team":{"id":13,"url":"https://hackerone.com/security","handle":"security","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/000/013/fa942b9b1cbf4faf37482bf68458e1195aab9c02_original.png/43e4513b9104ea0d68c9c096cea374ba8440dde3e027af5465c8771e8839a67c","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/000/013/fa942b9b1cbf4faf37482bf68458e1195aab9c02_original.png/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"permissions":[],"submission_state":"open","default_currency":"usd","awards_miles":false,"offers_bounties":true,"state":"public_mode","only_cleared_hackers":false,"pentest_feature_enabled?":false,"profile":{"name":"HackerOne","twitter_handle":"Hacker0x01","website":"https://hackerone.com","about":"Vulnerability disclosure should be safe, transparent, and rewarding."}},"has_bounty?":true,"in_validation?":false,"rejected_anc_report_that_can_be_sent_back_to_anc_triagers?":false,"can_view_team":true,"can_view_report":true,"is_external_bug":false,"is_published":false,"is_participant":false,"has_collaborators":false,"stage":4,"public":true,"visibility":"full","cve_ids":[],"singular_disclosure_disabled":false,"disclosed_at":"2014-10-28T23:18:36.550Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2014-10-28T22:31:48.413Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2014-10-28T23:18:36.257Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"The bug mentioned in #23386 is not yet correctly patched I believe.\r\n\r\nSee, if a user sets his/her profile's website link to a similar page as mentioned in #23386. I mean a page that can manipulate the window.opener property would be able to accomplish similar results as in #23386\r\n\r\n**Proof-of-Concept**:\r\n\r\n1. Login to HackerOne\r\n2. Navigate to https://hackerone.com/settings/profile/edit\r\n3. Set *Website* to https://demo.prakharprasad.com/ga.html\r\n4. Once someone visits this link from a profile page  (eg. https://hackerone.com/\u003cusername-\u003e), his opener HackerOne window will be hijacked.\r\n\r\nLet me know if you have any questions.\r\n\r\nThanks,\r\nPrakhar Prasad\r\n","bounty_amount":"500.0","formatted_bounty":"$500","original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":"2014-11-27T22:31:48.717Z","allow_singular_disclosure_after":-216835517.71882477,"singular_disclosure_allowed":true,"vote_count":2,"voters":["silv3rpoision","dyabla"],"structured_scope":null,"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"activities":[{"id":126427,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::BugTriaged","message":"Thank you for sending this in! This one seems trickier to fix, since we are not using the redirect interstitial here, which means that `window.opener = null;` won't suffice here. While we investigate other options, any ideas from your side are welcome as well! ","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2014-09-13T22:29:48.630Z","updated_at":"2014-09-13T22:29:48.630Z","actor":{"username":"michiel","cleared":true,"url":"/michiel","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/000/007/439427fb81f710e5e16246ede1828613d46bb79e_original.png/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":true},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"security","actor_is_team_member":true,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":126428,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"I believe it will be more neat if you can implement the redirect interstitial here. I strongly *think* that all external links originating from HackerOne, regardless of their origin (profile, bug report etc.) should go through a redirect interstitial. \n\nWhat's your take on this ?","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2014-09-13T22:36:50.513Z","updated_at":"2014-09-13T22:36:50.513Z","actor":{"username":"prakharprasad","cleared":true,"url":"/prakharprasad","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/4Qcsaci6HdNLQCPM7oBdhJYY/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"security","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":126429,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Yep, that is probably the most straightforward way to fix this. Another solution would be to remove the `target=\"_blank\"` in those links, so there is no `window.opener` to hijack. We'll discuss internally and will follow up shortly.","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2014-09-13T22:39:18.483Z","updated_at":"2014-09-13T22:39:18.483Z","actor":{"username":"michiel","cleared":true,"url":"/michiel","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/000/007/439427fb81f710e5e16246ede1828613d46bb79e_original.png/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":true},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"security","actor_is_team_member":true,"actor_is_concea